Hybrid strains are a cross of two or more strains of cannabis, allowing the patient to get the desired effects of both Indica and Sativa strains in one Hybrid strain. This Cali Kush concentrate is a great hybrid. Personally I felt more of the Indica feel (which I like) but for others, they felt more of the Sativa.

Cali Kush must have been a no-brainer when it came time to name this strain given the popularity of Kush varieties in the Golden State.
